\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 For most of us we want the same thing for us God wants for us:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Great marriages\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Great relationships with friends and family\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Finances secure and whole\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Health\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  The problem isn\'92t the end goal\'85it\'92s the way we get there:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Student who says I want to find the one but is only looking at one thing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s the spouse who says I want an amazing marriage but there are secrets and problems they don\'92t want to deal with\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s the person who wants financial freedom but doesn\'92t believe that giving away money leads to freedom.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s the person who says they want an exciting life with God but doesn\'92t want to take any the steps God puts in their paths.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 Most people talk to me about the will of God\'85yet I find most people already know what they are suppose to do they just don\'92t trust God enough to follow what He\'92s already said.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  there is a story in the Bible that helps us see what God is trying to teach each of us.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs24 \cf5 6\'a0
\f3\b0 \cf5 Now the gates of Jericho\'a0were securely barred because of the Israelites. No one went out and no one came in.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \super 2\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub Then the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua, \'93See, I have delivered\'a0Jericho into your hands, along with its king and its fighting men.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s amazing how two people can see the same situation completely differently.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some would look and see a secure fortress locked up with huge walls.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Others see a secure fortress locked up with huge walls\'85with terrified people inside.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question:  How do you see the situation in front of you?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  This is the moment that Joshua has been waiting for.  He\'92s been waiting for the words \'91Go\'92 and what he hears are specific instructions that don\'92t match any marching orders for war I\'92ve ever heard of.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf5 \'a0
\f0\b \super 3\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub March around the city once with all the armed men. Do this for six days.\'a0
\f0\b \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub Have seven priests carry trumpets of rams\'92 horns\'a0in front of the ark. On the seventh day, march around the city seven times, with the priests blowing the trumpets.\'a0
\f0\b \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub When you hear them sound a long blast\'a0on the trumpets, have the whole army give a loud shout;\'a0then the wall of the city will collapse and the army will go up, everyone straight in.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If this was me\'85I would have said, \'93Um God, you realize this isn\'92t a concert right?\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This feels more like marching band to me than it does battle!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God tells Joshua, \'93I want you to get all your men together\'85and go for a walk!\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If it is me \'96 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m worried about the walls and God is worried about the walk.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m worried about the battle and God\'92s worried about my obedience.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}At it\'92s core for many of us and I have to believe on some level for Joshua, there is a tension between what God wants for us, and how He wants us to get there.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want to talk about Walls, God wants to talk about our Walk\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For God the journey is just as important as the destination\'85sometimes more.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub When Joshua had spoken to the people, the seven priests carrying the seven trumpets before the\'a0Lord\'a0went forward, blowing their trumpets, and the ark of the\'a0Lord\'92s covenant followed them.\'a0
\f0\b \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub The armed guard marched ahead of the priests who blew the trumpets, and the rear guard\'a0followed the ark. All this time the trumpets were sounding.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Translation \'96 It is probably pretty loud\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub But Joshua had commanded the army, \'93Do not give a war cry, do not raise your voices, do not say a word until the day I tell you to shout. Then shout!\'94\'a0
\f0\b \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub So he had the ark of the\'a0Lord\'a0carried around the city, circling it once. Then the army returned to camp and spent the night there.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why does Joshua add the whole part about people talking?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because he knew there would be problems if people were talking the whole time\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine what some of the people were thinking while this was going on?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ll bet they were thinking this was crazy and wanted to talk about it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sometimes we can kill what God is doing in someone else because we talk to much.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}With my opinions I know I\'92ve killed things in people\'92s lives\'85I need to learn to keep my mouth shut because God may be doing something unique in their life that doesn\'92t make sense to anyone but the person God spoke to.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \super 20\'a0
\f1\b0 \nosupersub When the trumpets sounded,\'a0the army shouted, and at the sound of the trumpet, when the men gave a loud shout,\'a0the wall collapsed; so everyone charged straight in, and they took the city.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the easiest battle plan ever to follow\'85walk in a circle for a week and then move straight forward.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are two things God puts in your path for us to do:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The generic\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}These are hard but clear.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t sleep with people you\'92re not married to\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t steal from others\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t murder\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t Gossip or say bad things about others\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For you what is it?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The unique\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nic, I want you to quit your job and leave your family and move to a place far away from everyone you know to a place in MI\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nic I want you continue what you are doing but go back to school and get your undergraduate and then get a masters.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nic, I want you to start a church but it is going to be different and not like anything Glasgow has seen\'85and I want you to start it is a bowling alley!\
\pard\tx2380\tx2880\pardeftab720\li2880\fi-2880\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl3\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God do you know what people will say?  What people will think?\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For you what is it?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Next Right Steps\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit striving and trying to make things work\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Start focusing on your walk and not so much your walls\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sign up for our Outreach Team\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hand out the invite cards \'96 it may not make a lot of sense but we need to just do it.\
